it'd be my pleasure.

46:02.212 --> 46:20.752
What on Earth were we thinking,
giving you a weapon?

46:20.752 --> 46:29.212
Well done.

46:29.212 --> 46:31.132
Her temperature's down.

46:31.132 --> 46:32.464
Good.

46:32.464 --> 46:38.332
You are getting better.

46:38.332 --> 46:50.896
Monk?

46:50.896 --> 46:53.584
Here you are, lad,
give us a lug of that.

46:53.584 --> 46:56.212
I'm parched.

46:56.212 --> 47:12.292
Sharing's caring, man.

47:12.292 --> 47:14.896
We've finished this area.
About to move on, sir.

47:14.896 --> 47:17.456
Roger that, out.

47:17.456 --> 47:19.184
Colour.

47:19.184 --> 47:20.336
Boss.

47:20.336 --> 47:24.052
As soon as you've finished your
scoff, I want you, Fingers,

47:24.052 --> 47:26.692
Throbber to switch focus
to south of the village.

47:26.692 --> 47:30.384
Boss.

47:30.384 --> 47:31.984
Lane's moving shortly.

47:31.984 --> 47:57.904
We need to have eyes on
any potential threats.

47:57.904 --> 48:05.264
Bring me the list.

48:05.264 --> 48:09.052
Thank you.

48:09.052 --> 48:11.728
Lane, we have eyes on south village.

48:11.728 --> 48:16.016
Keep vigilant for threats
to Dr Bahil.

48:16.016 --> 48:20.692
Remember, compounds of
interest are...

48:20.692 --> 48:27.664
One five five, one two eight,
one one four, one seven nine.

48:27.664 --> 48:30.652
What's a compound of
interest, Colour?

48:30.652 --> 48:37.372
Known insurgent activity within.

48:37.372 --> 48:40.144
Antonio told me
you requested to join me.

48:40.144 --> 48:41.936
Thank you.

48:41.936 --> 48:45.968
Well, it was either do this
or my roots again.

48:45.968 --> 48:49.168
I shouldn't have said what I said
about your fiance.

48:49.168 --> 48:51.664
HORN HONKS

48:51.664 --> 48:54.928
I'm sure there's a part of you
that wants revenge.

48:54.928 --> 48:57.772
They shot my husband in the street
like a sick dog.

48:57.772 --> 49:00.944
Bang. Walked away.

49:00.944 --> 49:06.000
I'll get my revenge
by carrying on his work.

49:06.000 --> 49:08.240
My fiance was killed on
a mission to get Omar.

49:08.240 --> 49:10.864
And that's why Afghanistan
has drawn you back.

49:10.864 --> 49:12.912
No, they just send me here.

49:12.912 --> 49:15.984
The British Army is all over the
world and you chose to come here.

49:15.984 --> 49:17.968
It's just chance.

49:17.968 --> 49:19.252
You volunteered.

49:19.252 --> 49:43.376
These things don't happen by chance.

49:43.376 --> 49:47.664
Sir, Giti's gone. Her bed's empty.
Where is she?

49:47.664 --> 49:49.456
Is she not on the ward?

49:49.456 --> 49:51.504
Maybe someone's taken her
to the wash block.

49:51.504 --> 49:53.488
Her uncle came.

49:53.488 --> 49:55.024
What do you mean her uncle came?

49:55.024 --> 49:56.496
He took her.

49:56.496 --> 49:57.776
Well, he can't just take her

49:57.776 --> 49:59.824
cos she's not ready
to be discharged yet.

49:59.824 --> 50:02.256
She needs 24-hour care,
he can't just take her.

50:02.256 --> 50:09.424
Well, he saw a sign. Your sign.

50:09.424 --> 50:11.216
Is he allowed to just take her, sir?

50:11.216 --> 50:15.568
What can we do if the family
decide to take her home?

50:15.568 --> 50:20.368
Did you even try and persuade him
not to take her?

50:20.368 --> 50:22.612
How do we know that
she's being looked after?

50:22.612 --> 50:25.424
Cos we don't know where she is so
she could have been taken anywhere.

50:25.424 --> 50:28.304
What are we going to do?
We carry on.

50:28.304 --> 50:47.760
Get on with your duties, soldier.

50:47.760 --> 51:12.892
INAUDIBLE

51:12.892 --> 51:15.088
Straight to zero.
We're losing the light.

51:15.088 --> 51:16.852
Security vehicles will be monitoring

51:16.852 --> 51:25.372
and following once you're
outside the town. Out.

51:25.372 --> 51:28.612
Infidel!

51:28.612 --> 51:44.592
INDISTINCT SHOUTING

51:44.592 --> 51:50.332
One zero bravo to one zero alpha.
Dusk closing in. Prepare to move.

51:50.332 --> 51:52.784
I need you withdrawing
and heading back to zero, over.

51:52.784 --> 51:57.456
Roger that. Out.

51:57.456 --> 51:59.184
We need to head straight to zero.

51:59.184 --> 52:01.808
You're not allowed to leave
the vehicle for any reason.

52:01.808 --> 52:10.768
It's getting dark soon
and they won't have eyes on.

52:10.768 --> 52:12.688
Sir. Excuse me, sir.

52:12.688 --> 52:14.288
There's one particular moped.

52:14.288 --> 52:17.332
It's been following them.

52:17.332 --> 52:20.816
I clocked it a while ago.

52:20.816 --> 52:22.612
Stay in the vehicle.

52:22.612 --> 52:24.656
Go straight to zero...
STATIC ON RADIO

52:24.656 --> 52:29.520
Stay near the...

52:29.520 --> 52:31.824
You're being followed.
Leave immediately.

52:31.824 --> 52:34.640
I repeat, leave immediately.

52:34.640 --> 52:39.056
Nice one, Prof.

52:39.056 --> 52:41.332
It's the woman from the other day
at the school.

52:41.332 --> 52:44.752
With the irate husband.

52:44.752 --> 52:48.656
No, don't...

52:48.656 --> 52:50.256
Sir, they've got out.

52:50.256 --> 52:56.144
Stay in the vehicle, keep moving.
Repeat, stay in the vehicle, over.

52:56.144 --> 53:00.652
Suspect following on foot, sir.

53:00.652 --> 53:01.904
She's not responding.

53:01.904 --> 53:06.128
Sir, Lane has company -
and they're armed.

53:06.128 --> 53:08.176
We need to get to the village now.

53:08.176 --> 53:09.776
Everybody on me.

53:09.776 --> 53:15.664
Let's double away -
zeros, fives and twenties.

53:15.664 --> 53:17.264
She wants us to inoculate
her children.

53:17.264 --> 53:18.892
Get the bag and let's do it quickly.

53:18.892 --> 53:21.172
Poya, stay close.
I'll be right there.

53:21.172 --> 53:22.972
Monk, let's go.

53:22.972 --> 53:50.608
Lane. Lane, multiple insurgents
approaching. Do you copy?

53:50.608 --> 53:59.092
Sir. Sir, we need to get
to Georgie and Dr Bahil.

53:59.092 --> 54:12.112
Bag.

54:12.112 --> 54:22.992
There are two children here.
I'll inoculate them.

54:22.992 --> 54:26.256
She has a fractured eye socket.
We need to get her to a hospital.

54:26.256 --> 54:27.772
Not our immediate business.

54:27.772 --> 54:29.264
Shall we take her and the children?

54:29.264 --> 54:34.064
We cannot interfere in their lives.

54:34.064 --> 54:35.216
GUN COCKS

