54:52.752 --> 55:00.240
Shit.

55:00.240 --> 55:03.120
Throbber, easy!

55:03.120 --> 55:05.744
Follow me. Keep low.

55:05.744 --> 55:07.612
GUNFIRE

55:07.612 --> 55:18.416
We're being ambushed. Move. Move!

55:18.416 --> 55:22.640
HURST:At least five insurgents
surrounding Lane.

55:22.640 --> 55:26.096
Engage at will!

55:26.096 --> 55:28.912
We have to get them
back to the vehicle!

55:28.912 --> 55:40.624
Right, move, move, move.

55:40.624 --> 55:43.132
Throbber, they're round that corner!

55:43.132 --> 55:45.172
Coming through, coming through!

55:45.172 --> 55:48.652
GUNFIRE

55:48.652 --> 55:52.528
Prof on me! On me!

55:52.528 --> 56:07.252
Order, order, protect Georgie!

56:07.252 --> 56:10.384
I'm pinned down!

56:10.384 --> 56:15.824
Keep your head down. Move them away!
        Keep to the door!

56:15.824 --> 56:21.136
Come on!

56:21.136 --> 56:23.120
Clear!

56:23.120 --> 56:25.104
Right, let's move. Move!
SHE GASPS

56:25.104 --> 56:27.216
Right, come, come.
Follow me, follow me.

56:27.216 --> 56:31.696
Monk! Kingy! On Lane! On Lane!

56:31.696 --> 56:32.720
INDISTINCT SHOUTING

56:32.720 --> 56:35.984
Stay down.

56:35.984 --> 56:40.656
Clear the alley, clear the alley!

56:40.656 --> 56:43.492
MAN YELLS

56:43.492 --> 56:48.532
Clear! Move, move, move!
Right, let's go.

56:48.532 --> 56:53.392
Kingy, on Lane!

56:53.392 --> 56:56.464
GUNFIRE CONTINUES

