57:06.292 --> 57:09.456
Prof, on me!

57:09.456 --> 57:16.496
All clear. Get her to the vehicle.

57:16.496 --> 57:20.212
Get in the car. Get in.

57:20.212 --> 57:23.932
Poya... Wait!

57:23.932 --> 57:28.464
Where are you going?!

57:28.464 --> 57:32.112
Poya! She's gone! They've got her!

